data.eml:eml: Checklist of the adult nematode parasites of fishes in freshwater localities from Mexico

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Garrido-Olvera, Lorena, García-Prieto, Luis, León, Gerardo Pérez-Ponce De (2006): Checklist of the adult nematode parasites of fishes in freshwater localities from Mexico. Zootaxa 1201: 1-45, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.273411
